Properties.Description:
The Credit Status of the Party, Customer or Customer Account for the associated period.

Ex:
- Excellent / Pays On Time
- Above Average / Pays Within Acceptable Timeframe
- Average / Occasional Late Payments
- Below Average / Frequent Late Payments 
- Poor / Delinquent Activity
- Restricted / Collections or Legal Action Pending Or In-process
- Unrated
